{"tid":2276811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[我放心了]雷鼎鳴料拜登上台後　中美貿易戰將趨緩和","createTime":"2020-11-08T04:57:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T06:29:47.000Z","uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"67103250c171f6a4c13ecb72e70268d12c7ef58e","tid":2276811,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:57:57.000Z","msg":"代表民主黨參加美國總統大選的拜登發表全國演說，宣稱自己勝出並獲得創紀錄7400萬的授權票當選。<br />\n<br />\n科技大學經濟學系<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>前</strong></span>系主任雷鼎鳴說，相信拜登上台後，中美貿易戰將較為緩和。他指出，民主黨支持者均反對爭取連任的特朗普相關政策，預計拜登有機會降低關稅。另外，亦會縮減美國與其他盟國的貿易戰規模。<br />\n<br />\n雷鼎鳴提到，美國第3季國內生產總值即使有改善，但第2季數字跌幅太多，失業人數亦增加，相信美國總統未來主要任務是自我療傷。不過他對拜登的財政政策並不樂觀，因為民主黨政策傾向加稅，以及擴大政府開支，相信他的招數有限或會繼續「加印銀紙」，亦不會減稅，美國人負擔可能會更大。<br />\n<br />\n雷鼎鳴又說，美國對香港實施的經濟限制有限，由香港生產出口至美國的貨值，僅每年約5億美元，在國際上只是一個小數字。而目前對個別香港官員作出制裁是「姿態大於實際」，對香港經濟並無影響，美國未來會否取消有關制裁則視乎中美關係。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558918-20201108.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558918-20201108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ltJnWG3kir489%2BLnRwft23s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=e90bfe5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1558918-20201108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=152a1d1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1558918-20201108.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"4bb5552d136fee8e7327b4160d3ae33f3258e29f","tid":2276811,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:58:55.000Z","msg":"同關稅華一樣，完全無國際sense，你班on9咁講我就更加放心"},{"pid":"018d275210917d3b9ffb245b6b7ef67102461343","tid":2276811,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:59:30.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">中國成最大贏家<br />\n<br />\n習近平永續帝位</span>"},{"pid":"a9e223caff4960889b96dd74f79231374c82a144","tid":2276811,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"佢地既世界真係非黑即白得好緊要"},{"pid":"b33b3d96a8b878549cfcd069556ce25cdd5acd1a","tid":2276811,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:00:29.000Z","msg":"西教授可以用手機支付到美國叫雞了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9678dc440b1afab3b420d3fb5ed88320066db102","tid":2276811,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9e223caff4960889b96dd74f79231374c82a144","tid":2276811,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T04:59:58.000Z","msg":"佢地既世界真係非黑即白得好緊要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:01:40.000Z","msg":"支那劇入骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a9e650dd7b90ddb4d03755d45697b820867791","tid":2276811,"uid":54516,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"嗰時話佔中令香港損失3500億。<br />\n其實嗰時點做到科大經濟系系主任？"},{"pid":"198cb809b8b874f00483d83f24223916165b98dc","tid":2276811,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95a9e650dd7b90ddb4d03755d45697b820867791","tid":2276811,"uid":54516,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"嗰時話佔中令香港損失3500億。<br />\n其實嗰時點做到科大經濟系系主任？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:03:01.000Z","msg":"比紅包掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e5cab10a60ab2cb497addd09f7cd4d5b903613","tid":2276811,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:13:55.000Z","msg":"究竟雷鼎鳴有無tip中過一次?"},{"pid":"2d2f25e0183f0a80bb7adb5c6208a35591301524","tid":2276811,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95a9e650dd7b90ddb4d03755d45697b820867791","tid":2276811,"uid":54516,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"嗰時話佔中令香港損失3500億。<br